        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1932877303" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8653452759904335968">I read the Project Gutenberg edition that is translated by Denis Florence MacCarthy which is fabulous. He finds a unique voice for each character and maintains excellent dramatic tension throughout. He finishes with a marvelous rendition of Sigismund&apos;s monologue. </span>
  <span id="freeText8653452759904335968" style="display:none">I read the Project Gutenberg edition that is translated by Denis Florence MacCarthy which is fabulous. He finds a unique voice for each character and maintains excellent dramatic tension throughout. He finishes with a marvelous rendition of Sigismund's monologue. </span>
